                <mxCell id="flow-legend" value="&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;요청 흐름 (Request Flow)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;① Operator → CloudFront 접속 (TLS)&lt;br style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;② CloudFront + Lambda@Edge 인증 (RS256/PKCE) → VPC Origin → 내부 ALB&lt;br style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;③ ALB → Fargate web (Next.js thin-BFF)&lt;br style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;④ Fargate web ↔ Aurora Serverless v2 (node-pg, 상태 저장)&lt;br style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;⑤ Fargate web → AgentCore Runtime → 9개 Gateway → MCP 도구&lt;br style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;⑥ Fargate web → SQS → dispatcher → Step Functions → Fargate worker (비동기)&lt;br style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;⑦ MCP 도구 → EKS / Prometheus / Loki / CloudWatch (읽기 전용 조회)" style="rounded=1;arcSize=3;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FAFAFA;strokeColor=#879196;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontFamily=Amazon Ember;fontSize=13;fontColor=#232F3E;spacingTop=8;spacingLeft=8;spacingRight=8;" parent="aws-cloud" vertex="1">
